          Storage domain name cannot be empty. It can only consist of alphanumeric characters (that is, letters, numbers, and signs "-" and "_"). All other characters are not valid in the name.
          Please provide storage domain name. [hosted_storage]: hosted_storage
          Storage domain name cannot be empty. It can only consist of alphanumeric characters (that is, letters, numbers, and signs "-" and "_"). All other characters are not valid in the name.

